      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your <strong>chicken </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut </strong>and <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>in 225ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
