            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is cooking, trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely on the diagonal</p><p>Top, tail and peel your <strong>mango[es]</strong></p><p>Stand the <strong>mango[es]</strong> upright and very carefully slice the flesh away from the <strong>stone[s]</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>mango</strong> <strong>flesh</strong> roughly, discarding the stone[s]</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1680603764943-x200.jpg",
