            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped mango </strong>and <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>in a bowl with the <strong>lime zest</strong>, the juice of <strong>half </strong>you <strong>lime[s]</strong>, the <strong>chopped coriander</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>mango salsa</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
