            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Caribbean-style</strong> <strong>spiced chicken </strong>over<strong> </strong>the <strong>coconut rice </strong>with the <strong>mango salsa </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
